name: Shortcut
description:
A Pine Squirrel proudly investigates security of the hidden shortcut entrance to it's winter den in a log pile buried under the snow. (Tamiasciurus hudsonicus)

2017. Nikon D60, 55-200mm Lens.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing.

1024x685 300dpi jpeg
